title Action Tile

user->UI: Click Spin
UI->logic: Spin message
logic->logic: compute roll
logic->logic: land on action tile
logic->logic: draw action card from deck
logic->UI: inform user of action card
alt pay player card
    logic->UI: request target
    user->UI: select target
    UI->logic: pass on selection
else otherwise
    logic->logic: perform action on card
end
logic->UI: turn over/status update
user->UI: acknowledge turn end
UI->logic: ack. message
logic->logic: next player
